  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110177989596\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110177989596\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:9pt; font-family:'3028548_9';\" class=\"view\"><div style=\"font-size:9pt; font-family:'3028548_9';\" class=\"view\"> \r\n<div class=\"view\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><font size=\"2\"><b><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">자궁근종이란 자궁 근육에<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span>생기는 양성종양으로<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span>크고 작은 동그란 모양으로 생기고 갯수도 한 개부터 여러 개까지<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span>다양하게 생길 수 있다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span></span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-no-proof: yes\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (v:shapetype) --><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (v:stroke) --><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (v:formulas) --><!-- Not Allowed Tag Filtered --><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (v:shape) --><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (v:imagedata) --></span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/90f1f161780cb6b5.jpg\" width=\"227\" height=\"222\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 227px; rheight: 222px\" id=\"20131018_101/isuhani_1382062027588WnpNk_JPEG/%C0%DA%B1%C3%B1%D9%C1%BE_%C0%A7%C4%A1.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A71EB3DC')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/90f1f161780cb6b5.jpg\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" />&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">&nbsp;<!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><font size=\"2\"><b><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">자궁근종은 크기가 크지 않으면 증상이 나타나지 않기 때문에 본인도 모르는 채 지내는 수가 많으며 우연히 발견되는 경우가 대부분이다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span></span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><font size=\"2\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: red; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">30</span></b><b><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: red; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">세 이상 여성의<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 20%</span>가 자궁근종을 가지고 있다<span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span></span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><font size=\"2\"><b><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">그러니까 여성에게 가장 많이</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Courier New'; COLOR: red; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 굴림\">&#65279;</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"> </span></b><b><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">생기는 혹이 자궁근종이라고 해도 지나친 말은 아니다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span></span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><font size=\"2\"><b><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">근종의 크기가 커지면 생리양이 많아지고 피가 덩어리져서 나오면서 빈혈 증상이 겹치게 된다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span></span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">&nbsp;<!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><font size=\"2\"><b><u><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">젊은 여성에게 자궁근종이 생길 경우 수정란이 착상되는 것을 방해하여 불임증을 일으킬 수도 있고<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>임신이 되더라도 유산이나 조산이 될 수 있다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span></span></u></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">&nbsp;<!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt\"><b><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; LINE-HEIGHT: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><font size=\"2\">증상은 자궁근종의 크기와 비례하므로 근종의 크기는 평소에 확인하여 알고 있는 것이 좋다<span lang=\"EN-US\">.<!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></font></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; LINE-HEIGHT: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --><font size=\"2\">&nbsp;</font></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><b><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">자궁근종은 자궁의 여러부위에서 발생하기 때문에 생긴 위치에 따라 점막하근종<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>점막내근종<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>장막하근종 등으로 나뉜다<span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span></span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><b><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">내진을 하면 자궁근종을 쉽게 확인할 수 있으며<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>초음파 검사를 하면 근종이 생긴 부위와 크기를 정확히 알아낼 수 있다<span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span></span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">&nbsp;<!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-no-proof: yes\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (v:shape) --><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (v:imagedata) --></span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">&nbsp;<img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20131018_204/isuhani_1382062027886JgsSd_JPEG/%C0%DA%B1%C3%B1%D9%C1%BE.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"205\" height=\"182\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 205px; rheight: 182px\" id=\"20131018_204/isuhani_1382062027886JgsSd_JPEG/%C0%DA%B1%C3%B1%D9%C1%BE.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A71EB3DC')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20131018_204/isuhani_1382062027886JgsSd_JPEG/%C0%DA%B1%C3%B1%D9%C1%BE.jpg?type=w3\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><b><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">자궁근종은 양성종양이므로 크기가 작고 증상이 없으면 별다른 치료를 받지 않아도 된다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span></span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><b><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">그러나 하혈 등의 증상이 있으면 치료를 받는게 좋으며 한약치료로 좋은 효과를 얻을 수 있다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span></span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><b><u><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: red; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">실제로 자궁근종으로 하혈이 심하고<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>생리통이 있고<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>그로인해 기운이 없고 어지러운 환자분들을 종종 치료하게 되는데<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>한약을 복용하면서 침치료를 병행하면 한달이내에 하혈도 줄고 기운도 나는 것을 경험한다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span></span></u></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">&nbsp;<span style=\"mso-no-proof: yes\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (v:shape) --> </span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><span style=\"mso-no-proof: yes\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (v:shape) --></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><span style=\"mso-no-proof: yes\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (v:shape) --><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (v:imagedata) --></span><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f505ab2eac3644a5.png\" width=\"550\" height=\"541\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 728px\" id=\"20131018_156/isuhani_1382062062919re44S_PNG/%C0%DA%B1%C3%B1%D9%C1%BE_%C4%A1%C7%E8%B7%CA.png\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A71EB3DC')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f505ab2eac3644a5.png\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-left: 0gd; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore\">-<span style=\"FONT: 7pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">한약 치료 후 자궁근종 환자의 증상 및 근종 크기 변화 <span lang=\"EN-US\">&#8211; </span>대한한방부인과학회지 <span lang=\"EN-US\">VOL.18, NO.4 : 230-241 (2005)<!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) -->&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><b><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">자궁근종을 수술 해야 하는가의 문제에서 크기는 중요치 않다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>크기가 몇 센티 이상이라 해서 수술을 해야 한다는 기준은 없고<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>다만 몇 가지 가이드 라인이 있다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>다만 근종의 크기가 <span lang=\"EN-US\">7-8cm</span>을 넘어가면 수술을 고려하는게 일반적이다<span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span></span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">&nbsp;<!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">1) </span></b><b><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">비정상적 자궁출혈 때문에 빈혈이 오고<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>심각하게 헤모글로빈 수치가 낮아지는 경우</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">2) </span></b><b><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">월경과다<span lang=\"EN-US\">(hypermenorrhea)</span>를 동반한 점막하근종</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">3) </span></b><b><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">유경성근종<span lang=\"EN-US\">( </span>자궁혹에 줄기가 있는 근종<span lang=\"EN-US\"> )</span></span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">4) </span></b><b><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">방광이나 직장이 근종에 의하여 압박증상이 나타날 때</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">5) </span></b><b><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">광간막근종<span lang=\"EN-US\">( </span>골반안의 인대사이로 근종이 돌출되어 끼어 있을 때<span lang=\"EN-US\"> )</span></span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">6) </span></b><b><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">골반염<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>자궁내막증과 같이 다른 골반질환이 동반되었을 때</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">7) </span></b><b><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">근종이 급히 자랄 때</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">&nbsp;<!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">&nbsp;<!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><b><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">젊은 여성의 경우 자궁근종 때문에 불임이 유발될 때는 수술을 하기도 한다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span></span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><b><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">그러나 자궁근종과 불임과의 연관성은 명확하게 밝혀지질 않았다. 다만 다른 원인이 밝혀지지 않은 불임화자의 경우 근종 절제술 후 임신 여부로 간접적으로 평가되고 있다. 대체로 자궁근종을 가진 여성의 5~10%에서 불임과 연관이 있으며, 그 중 2%에서는 자궁근종 자체가 불임을 초래하는 것으로 알려져 있다. </span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><b><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">자궁근종이 불임을 초래하는 원인으로는 근종이 정상적인 자궁수축력을 방해하고, 자궁의 변형과 해부학적 용적의 증가를 가져와 정자수송을 방해하며, 자궁경부의 위치 변화로 자궁경부 내구폐쇄 및 난관 간질부 압박으로 인한 난관폐쇄를 일으킨다는 것과 자궁내막이 위축되거나 과증식되어 혈관의 변조가 착상을 방해할 수 있다고 설명하고 있다. </span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><b><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"></span></b><b><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">자궁근종 절제술 후 임신성공률은 보통<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;40-50% </span>정도로 보고된다. </span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><b><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">한 연구에서는 자궁근종 절제술 후 임신이 성공한 산모 중 28.1%가 자연유산이 되었다고 보고하였다.</span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><b><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"></span></b><b><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">따라서 <span style=\"COLOR: red\">수술 전에 한방치료 등의 비수술적 방법을 시도해보도록 권하고 싶다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>실제 한방치료로<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span>근종의 크기도 줄고 임신이 성공하는 경우들이 많다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span></span></span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/7b86ffd1f6bd8d58.jpg\" width=\"263\" height=\"192\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 263px; rheight: 192px\" id=\"20131018_118/isuhani_1382062168657v4PjJ_JPEG/imagesCA1PKF00.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A71EB3DC')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/7b86ffd1f6bd8d58.jpg\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"WORD-BREAK: keep-all; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 8pt; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-no-proof: yes\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (v:shape) --><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (v:imagedata) --></span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" s